Message:
Thank you for the beautiful dream.
It allowed me to remember.

Our two swords,
interchained with one oath.
There is nothing more we need.

Yes. This is a dream.
A phantom of the night.

A cheap play full of nonsense,
wafting in the heat of midsummer.

And with that, a clichéd line
would serve well to draw
the curtain on this stage.

Ophelia. Although I say
these words to your imposter,

the feelings I put into them
bear no lies.
